(A rainbow at every turn)

3
00:01:59,176 --> 00:02:00,293
Hi, Little boy

4
00:02:00,941 --> 00:02:02,504
No rainbows today, huh?

5
00:02:03,907 --> 00:02:07,172
I passed by here in the evening soon after she was born

6
00:02:08,938 --> 00:02:13,149
It was winter, but suddenly there was a rainbow over the lake

7
00:02:13,477 --> 00:02:16,258
Oh really?
Rainbows in winter are rare

8
00:02:16,360 --> 00:02:17,352
Yes true

9
00:02:18,563 --> 00:02:21,235
The colors of that rainbow were like spring and summer

10
00:02:22,680 --> 00:02:25,891
When I see a big rainbow, I feel like happiness is coming

11
00:02:27,953 --> 00:02:29,922
I showed it to this kid

12
00:02:30,508 --> 00:02:31,719
He didn't seem to get it

13
00:02:31,907 --> 00:02:33,250
Because he's a little boy

14
00:02:33,953 --> 00:02:35,422
How old is he now?

15
00:02:35,649 --> 00:02:37,633
He is 5 month plus a few months years old

16
00:02:44,141 --> 00:02:45,107
Would you excuse me a minute?

17
00:02:46,654 --> 00:02:48,022
I will take care of him

18
00:02:48,147 --> 00:02:49,537
Can you?
Thank you very much

19
00:03:06,115 --> 00:03:06,756
Chu chu

20
00:03:14,264 --> 00:03:15,561
Thank you very much

21
00:03:17,139 --> 00:03:18,279
Shall I do it for you?

22
00:03:18,311 --> 00:03:19,475
I'm used to it

23
00:03:23,061 --> 00:03:24,107
ooh-la-la!

24
00:03:26,717 --> 00:03:28,889
His mother is in Kyoto now

25
00:03:31,139 --> 00:03:32,279
Have you ever taken care of a baby?

26
00:03:32,857 --> 00:03:33,748
No No

27
00:03:34,084 --> 00:03:35,787
But I learnt it at school

28
00:03:35,818 --> 00:03:36,897
Oh! at school!

29
00:03:36,982 --> 00:03:37,662
Yes

30
00:03:37,772 --> 00:03:41,139
Someone'll make you do it soon enough

31
00:03:45,045 --> 00:03:47,311
Well..Are you living in Tokyo?

32
00:03:47,670 --> 00:03:49,654
Yes,
I had some business in Kyoto

33
00:03:49,865 --> 00:03:51,287
I'm on the way to return to Tokyo

34
00:03:51,334 --> 00:03:52,881
I see, I understand

35
00:03:54,225 --> 00:03:56,147
Oh,lalalala

36
00:04:18,810 --> 00:04:19,513
Stop here

37
00:04:31,318 --> 00:04:32,482
Why did you go to Kyoto?

38
00:04:32,998 --> 00:04:36,334
I went to see my friend who got married

39
00:04:36,623 --> 00:04:37,475
You are lying

40
00:04:37,943 --> 00:04:38,881
I'm not lying

41
00:04:40,897 --> 00:04:42,529
But the real purpose is different

42
00:04:46,826 --> 00:04:50,045
The sister that you went to look for, did you find her in Kyoto?

43
00:04:51,787 --> 00:04:52,732
Did you find her?

44
00:04:56,115 --> 00:04:56,748
I see

45
00:04:58,131 --> 00:05:00,990
I think She's lucky you didn't find her

46
00:05:01,334 --> 00:05:04,334
Sister,
Our father does not know about it at all

47
00:05:04,803 --> 00:05:06,639
Asako went to Kyoto with that in mind

48
00:05:07,803 --> 00:05:08,826
I can't say

49
00:05:13,209 --> 00:05:14,451
Our father has a good intuition

50
00:05:15,193 --> 00:05:16,451
I also have a good intuition

51
00:05:16,772 --> 00:05:17,982
What did our father say?

52
00:05:18,443 --> 00:05:20,037
He didn't say anything

53
00:05:24,647 --> 00:05:26,951
For whom did you go to Kyoto?

54
00:05:27,529 --> 00:05:28,647
For our father?

55
00:05:29,154 --> 00:05:30,623
Or for us?

56
00:05:31,615 --> 00:05:33,553
For your mother? or

57
00:05:34,654 --> 00:05:35,842
For the sister in Kyoto?

58
00:05:37,162 --> 00:05:39,287
It's not for anyone

59
00:05:40,357 --> 00:05:42,217
So did you feel morally responsible?

60
00:05:43,748 --> 00:05:45,162
If not, For your viewing pleasure?

61
00:05:47,834 --> 00:05:49,107
I don't know...

62
00:05:53,029 --> 00:05:57,561
Before Asako's mother died, she was worried about her child in Kyoto

63
00:05:58,904 --> 00:06:00,178
So you went there?

64
00:06:02,975 --> 00:06:03,514
But..

65
00:06:03,553 --> 00:06:06,350
I'm sorry I need to leave now

66
00:06:23,037 --> 00:06:24,240
Sister

67
00:06:24,912 --> 00:06:25,681
I have a favor of you.

68
00:06:25,705 --> 00:06:29,178
Please don't make a distinction
between Asako's mother and your mother.

69
00:06:30,326 --> 00:06:33,178
Asako's mother is your mother now

70
00:06:33,607 --> 00:06:34,607
I hope you understand

71
00:06:35,584 --> 00:06:36,420
Right

72
00:06:37,404 --> 00:06:39,357
She was very nice

73
00:06:41,388 --> 00:06:44,513
I had a mother of my own who committed suicide

74
00:06:44,764 --> 00:06:46,006
There is no choice to say it

75
00:06:48,693 --> 00:06:51,412
Don't cry.
You don't have to cry

76
00:06:58,248 --> 00:07:00,022
You are sweet,Asako

77
00:07:01,670 --> 00:07:04,006
You went to see her because you have feelings for your sister in Kyoto

78
00:07:06,178 --> 00:07:07,139
But Asako

79
00:07:08,389 --> 00:07:10,225
Before your mother die

80
00:07:10,873 --> 00:07:14,802
I don't know if she meant it when she acknowledged the girl from Kyoto as our sister

81
00:07:15,154 --> 00:07:16,826
Why do you think so?

82
00:07:17,068 --> 00:07:18,639
She's dying, herself...

83
00:07:19,748 --> 00:07:21,607
Asako's mother is miserable

84
00:07:22,529 --> 00:07:24,928
If the Kyoto kid comes into our house later

85
