86
00:07:30,100 --> 00:07:32,584
You are going to Kyoto for your mother

87
00:07:32,904 --> 00:07:33,959
You are stupid

88
00:07:34,014 --> 00:07:34,881
Sister...

89
00:07:36,506 --> 00:07:39,904
Everyone has their own way of life and their own environment

90
00:07:41,678 --> 00:07:45,818
I think the girl in Kyoto will be confused when they enter the house

91
00:07:46,717 --> 00:07:48,334
Brothers are just the beginning of strangers

92
00:07:48,951 --> 00:07:50,225
Let her do whatever she wants

93
00:08:33,068 --> 00:08:34,787
Go home!
Go home!

94
00:08:55,115 --> 00:08:56,772
Why aren't you waiting in your usual spot?

95
00:08:57,295 --> 00:08:58,936
I had been waiting you there

96
00:08:59,639 --> 00:09:02,232
Why are you snooping around my house like a thief?

97
00:09:02,443 --> 00:09:05,264
Because you often skip our dates

98
00:09:23,842 --> 00:09:25,365
Our father's car

99
00:10:07,873 --> 00:10:08,600
Where is Momoko?

100
00:10:08,943 --> 00:10:10,334
She has just let house

101
00:10:16,764 --> 00:10:17,873
Oh welcome home

102
00:10:18,068 --> 00:10:18,857
When did you back home?

103
00:10:18,936 --> 00:10:19,654
Just now

104
00:10:19,740 --> 00:10:20,943
Mmmm..
You must be tired

105
00:10:21,045 --> 00:10:22,147
Not at all

106
00:10:23,131 --> 00:10:24,537
Shall we prepare the meal?

107
00:10:27,615 --> 00:10:28,811
You haven't eaten yet, have you?

108
00:10:28,967 --> 00:10:29,459
Not yet

109
00:10:29,951 --> 00:10:31,881
I bought your favorite boiled rice soaked with tea

110
00:10:32,029 --> 00:10:33,787
Really? Thank you very much

111
00:10:36,795 --> 00:10:37,608
Please prepare a meal for him

112
00:10:37,740 --> 00:10:38,561
Yes

113
00:10:45,686 --> 00:10:47,170
Where are the hangers,Sumi?

114
00:10:57,295 --> 00:10:58,615
Was it cold in Kyoto?

115
00:10:58,904 --> 00:11:00,553
It was not cold much

116
00:11:04,475 --> 00:11:07,412
Miss, the spinach is cooked

117
00:11:07,670 --> 00:11:08,381
Did you drain it well?

118
00:11:08,444 --> 00:11:09,107
Yes

119
00:11:09,427 --> 00:11:10,849
Okay, you can cut up the bacon.

120
00:11:10,982 --> 00:11:11,373
Yes

121
00:11:11,544 --> 00:11:13,982
Then open a can of olive oil.

122
00:11:14,139 --> 00:11:14,779
Yes

123
00:11:18,029 --> 00:11:20,154
It's inconvenient and annoying without Asako

124
00:11:21,334 --> 00:11:22,217
For a meal

125
00:11:23,209 --> 00:11:24,803
and for everything

126
00:11:25,427 --> 00:11:27,091
Because my mother taught me

127
00:11:29,311 --> 00:11:33,537
I'm thinking of going to Atami for work in a couple of days

128
00:11:34,553 --> 00:11:35,303
Do you want to come with me?

129
00:11:35,420 --> 00:11:36,295
Yes I would like to go

130
00:11:36,959 --> 00:11:38,483
Shall we ask my sister too?

131
00:11:39,201 --> 00:11:39,826
Um

132
00:11:41,451 --> 00:11:44,381
But...I wonder she wants to come

133
00:11:54,256 --> 00:11:57,194
It's a tragedy to be thrown away after just a few peeks at your house

134
00:11:58,264 --> 00:11:59,404
What are you talking about?

135
00:12:00,342 --> 00:12:02,561
You're just passing through me

136
00:12:03,045 --> 00:12:04,279
Passing through you?

137
00:12:05,748 --> 00:12:07,811
You will like another student girl soon

138
00:12:08,451 --> 00:12:10,889
No way, you think so?

139
00:12:11,459 --> 00:12:13,561
I'd have to die if you left me

140
00:12:14,014 --> 00:12:14,740
I'm serious

141
00:12:14,850 --> 00:12:16,584
You don't have to say that

142
00:12:17,006 --> 00:12:19,678
So You don't get angry anymore?
Please promise it

143
00:12:21,537 --> 00:12:23,256
Ok, I do

144
00:12:23,459 --> 00:12:24,951
In exchange, I'll take you to Hakone

145
00:12:24,983 --> 00:12:25,678
Really?

146
00:12:26,404 --> 00:12:28,108
I'm glad,You really should take me to Hakone

147
00:12:48,990 --> 00:12:50,240
It's quiet here

148
00:12:50,475 --> 00:12:51,311
Yes

149
00:12:52,100 --> 00:12:54,553
You changed your mind suddenly

150
00:12:54,717 --> 00:12:56,194
You preferred Hakone to Atami

151
00:12:56,537 --> 00:12:59,029
I think this change would have been better

152
00:13:02,287 --> 00:13:03,662
Excuse me

153
00:13:05,725 --> 00:13:07,045
The bath is ready

154
00:13:07,592 --> 00:13:08,686
Oh, Thank you

155
00:13:10,459 --> 00:13:11,498
Shall we take a bath?

156
00:13:12,022 --> 00:13:13,287
I'm shy

157
00:13:13,552 --> 00:13:14,951
You will be shy with me?

158
00:13:15,076 --> 00:13:15,912
Because

159
00:13:17,342 --> 00:13:18,514
Then I will take first

160
00:13:18,608 --> 00:13:19,225
I see

161
00:13:26,694 --> 00:13:28,069
Ah...

162
00:13:33,069 --> 00:13:34,076
Father

163
00:13:35,498 --> 00:13:36,998
I will take a bath with you too

164
00:13:48,053 --> 00:13:49,233
I will go for a walk there

165
00:13:49,569 --> 00:13:50,131
Yes

166
00:13:55,959 --> 00:13:56,928
I will take care of your luggage

167
00:13:58,576 --> 00:13:59,225
Take care

168
00:14:06,436 --> 00:14:07,639
Ah...

169
00:14:08,717 --> 00:14:11,365
I'm going to build Asako a house

170
00:14:12,623 --> 00:14:13,631
My house?

171
00:14:14,576 --> 00:14:16,201
I will live there alone?

172
00:14:18,108 --> 00:14:20,295
Is there anyone you want to live with yet?

173
00:14:22,107 --> 00:14:22,967
I have no idea

174
00:14:25,334 --> 00:14:27,076
If so, you can live there alone

175
00:14:27,889 --> 00:14:30,670
A home worthy of your beauty

176
00:14:32,084 --> 00:14:33,584
I'm an architect

177
00:14:34,240 --> 00:14:35,936
Even in a small house for my daughter

178
00:14:36,803 --> 00:14:39,186
I want to leave you a house, like will testament

179
00:14:40,209 --> 00:14:41,897
A house like a will?

180
00:14:42,092 --> 00:14:43,568
I don't like it

181
00:14:45,709 --> 00:14:46,639
But listen to me

182
00:14:48,303 --> 00:14:51,475
Recently I feel something...

183
00:14:52,552 --> 00:14:56,404
I feel the fate of architects in the age of atomic and hydrogen bombs

184
00:14:56,514 --> 00:14:59,334
You say the loneliest things

185
00:15:00,912 --> 00:15:03,850
To build a house for my daughter...

186
00:15:04,592 --> 00:15:06,561
It's fatherly love

187
00:15:07,459 --> 00:15:08,545
or rather I should say

188
00:15:09,139 --> 00:15:10,694
It's a fatherly touch

189
00:15:11,185 --> 00:15:12,880
Yes, It's a fatherly touch

190
00:15:39,069 --> 00:15:39,670
Hey you

191
00:15:39,811 --> 00:15:40,295
Yes

192
00:15:40,819 --> 00:15:42,553
Where is the best view spot?

193
00:15:43,350 --> 00:15:45,584
It's a badminton court there

194
00:15:53,608 --> 00:15:54,397
Father

195
00:15:55,842 --> 00:15:56,233
Hum?

196
00:15:57,600 --> 00:16:00,170
You have three houses to build for your daughters

197
00:16:00,694 --> 00:16:01,030
What?

198
00:16:06,913 --> 00:16:07,983
For my sister

199
00:16:08,491 --> 00:16:09,999
For my younger sister in Kyoto too

200
00:16:12,420 --> 00:16:13,084
Oh

201
00:16:33,772 --> 00:16:34,303
Asako

202
00:16:35,272 --> 00:16:36,905
Don't go there, let's go back

203
00:16:48,577 --> 00:16:49,499
You know what?

204
00:16:51,131 --> 00:16:54,272
My sister thinks we've been to Atami

205
00:16:55,131 --> 00:16:57,811
It's like we're doing something wrong and hiding

206
00:16:59,030 --> 00:17:00,538
What are you going to do with my sister?

207
00:17:02,444 --> 00:17:04,225
Can you just leave my sister alone?

208
00:17:06,413 --> 00:17:07,538
Is that OK with you?

209
00:17:43,194 --> 00:17:43,874
Thanks for the meal

210
00:17:44,014 --> 00:17:44,709
Not at all

211
00:18:16,077 --> 00:18:18,913
She seduced such a young boy

212
00:18:21,342 --> 00:18:23,741
I don't understand what she thinks

213
00:18:27,045 --> 00:18:30,569
Find the real wound in Momoko's mind

214
00:18:32,077 --> 00:18:33,280
Find the real wound ?

215
00:18:34,163 --> 00:18:37,006
I don't know what to do too

216
00:18:40,123 --> 00:18:44,153
She would only confide in her real mother,I think...

217
00:18:45,209 --> 00:18:46,053
Who knows?

218
00:18:47,069 --> 00:18:49,991
And She's strong-minded

219
00:18:52,459 --> 00:18:53,264
But father....

220
00:18:53,334 --> 00:18:54,116
Asako

221
00:18:55,834 --> 00:18:59,256
I've been in love twice, married once

222
00:19:00,881 --> 00:19:02,686
Momoko is the child of my first love

223
00:19:04,288 --> 00:19:06,030
You are the child of the woman I married.

224
00:19:08,029 --> 00:19:10,499
And the last child, Wakako

225
00:19:21,991 --> 00:19:25,249
Am I dirty man?

226
00:19:30,913 --> 00:19:34,866
Anyway each my daughters are very beautiful

227
00:19:36,147 --> 00:19:38,944
Whenever I see you,I forget my sins

228
00:19:40,999 --> 00:19:42,975
That's just another selfish thought on my part

229
00:19:46,827 --> 00:19:49,467
I took Momoko in despite your mother's presence

230
00:19:50,194 --> 00:19:52,186
Because Momoko's mother committed suicide

231
00:19:54,475 --> 00:19:59,326
That may broke Momoko's heart

232
00:20:02,530 --> 00:20:04,280
You have 3 children

233
00:20:05,061 --> 00:20:07,850
In truth, I'm the only one

234
00:20:08,694 --> 00:20:09,436
You are right

235
00:20:10,733 --> 00:20:11,608
If so...

236
00:20:12,381 --> 00:20:14,084
I feel sorry for you

237
00:20:14,764 --> 00:20:15,717
But,Asako

238
00:20:16,866 --> 00:20:20,217
Children and parents cannot be separated from each other

239
00:20:22,420 --> 00:20:24,936
I would like to see my sister in Kyoto

240
00:20:26,545 --> 00:20:28,069
I want you to meet her

241
00:20:29,483 --> 00:20:31,202
But Momoko won't allow it

242
00:20:32,506 --> 00:20:33,631
Want to eat some?

243
00:20:40,249 --> 00:20:43,522
Who would take out a motorboat this late in the day?

244
00:21:05,905 --> 00:21:08,295
Close the door,Asako.
It's cold

245
00:21:19,038 --> 00:21:19,702
What's wrong?

246
00:21:20,811 --> 00:21:22,655
I thought that person was my sister

247
00:21:25,483 --> 00:21:28,217
But I don't see the boat. I only can hear the sound

248
00:21:28,842 --> 00:21:30,928
Are you thinking the same thing?

249
00:21:31,514 --> 00:21:32,811
The same thing?

250
00:21:34,155 --> 00:21:37,967
Momoko plays with dangerous men because she has bad experiences in the past

251
00:21:38,780 --> 00:21:42,577
Momoko resents that you're a filthy man

252
00:21:43,053 --> 00:21:43,639
So

253
00:21:43,664 --> 00:21:44,686
It might be so

254
00:21:45,514 --> 00:21:48,350
Whenever I've been watching her behavior

255
00:21:49,303 --> 00:21:52,663
I think she's willing to try to kill herself.

256
00:21:53,077 --> 00:21:53,803
kill herself?

257
00:22:03,475 --> 00:22:06,452
Father,Not only for my sister but

258
00:22:07,405 --> 00:22:11,366
What if I and my sister in Kyoto are three like my sister?

259
00:22:12,749 --> 00:22:15,186
Such as Suicide, hating their father,

260
00:22:15,920 --> 00:22:17,717
being far away from you

261
00:22:17,772 --> 00:22:19,241
What are you talking about,Asako?

262
00:22:20,224 --> 00:22:21,920
I don't like our current situation

263
00:22:22,194 --> 00:22:23,045
We are sister

264
00:22:23,186 --> 00:22:25,569
I want everyone to be happy

265
00:23:05,288 --> 00:23:09,225
Oh,I wondered who you were, but I guess you're Mizuhara.

266
00:23:09,288 --> 00:23:10,295
It's been a whole

267
00:23:10,397 --> 00:23:12,334
You came here all of a sudden

268
00:23:12,366 --> 00:23:13,006
Yes

269
00:23:13,116 --> 00:23:14,600
Anyway Please come in

270
00:23:27,077 --> 00:23:28,381
Nothing has changed here

271
00:23:28,530 --> 00:23:29,420
No way

272
00:23:29,647 --> 00:23:31,858
I don't take much care of it

273
00:23:33,061 --> 00:23:35,420
You came here alone tonight?

274
00:23:35,670 --> 00:23:37,452
No.
We came here with my daughters

275
00:23:37,592 --> 00:23:39,202
I see.
That would be nice

276
00:23:40,499 --> 00:23:43,217
There is someone who wants to build a tea house here

277
00:23:43,342 --> 00:23:44,834
I came here for the work

278
00:23:44,866 --> 00:23:45,717
I see

279
00:23:52,772 --> 00:23:54,905
In fact, I wanted to meet Kikue

280
00:23:55,475 --> 00:23:56,108
What?

281
00:23:56,327 --> 00:23:58,428
I used to come here with her

